rows.label: tlk45500153_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Here's a bit of gossip I heard
at the baths.

rows.label: tlk45500153_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently nobody's seen hide
nor hair of the Emperor's personal
Blade around here lately.

rows.label: tlk45500153_05_msg0003
rows.name:
There are all sorts of wild rumors
about where he could have gone.

rows.label: tlk45500153_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Saying he's been sent to assassinate
the Queen of Invidia, or that he was sent
to marry her as a sign of goodwill!
